title: A set of equipment for the production of polyethylene bags (Model B) US-SJ-60/FM 1000

title_en: A set of equipment for the production of polyethylene bags (Model B) US-SJ-60/FM 1000
short_description: This equipment for the production of polyethylene bags belongs to the US-SJ-60/FM 1000 model and has a production capacity of 50 kg to 100 kg per hour. The thickness of the film is 0.008-0.10 mm, the weight of the equipment is 3500 kg and the size is 5.0 * 3.0 * 6.2 m. There are other models of this equipment in the description below, and their prices vary depending on the model.
short_description_uz: Polietilen paketlar ishlab chiqarish jarayonini amalga oshiruvchi ushbu uskuna US-SJ-60/FM 1000 modelida mansub va soatiga 50 kg dan 100 kg gacha mahsulot ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega. Plyonka qalinligi 0.008-0.10 mm, uskunaning vazni 3500 kg va o'lchami 5.0 * 3.0 * 6.2 m ni tashkil qiladi. Quyidagi tavsifda shu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham mavjud va ularning narxlari modellariga qarab farqlanadi.
